00:56:55.730 --> 00:56:57.093
I'm nobody's rebound.

759
00:57:03.360 --> 00:57:04.443
- Hey, wait!

760
00:57:08.360 --> 00:57:10.213
- Leave me alone you fucking psycho!

761
00:57:24.713 --> 00:57:26.546
- Why did you do that?

762
