(ominous music)
- I'm here to protect you.


765
00:57:39.260 --> 00:57:40.920
- [Ashley] Okay. So now what?

766
00:57:40.920 --> 00:57:44.033
You have me here. You convinced
me Mandy deserved to die.


767
00:57:45.980 --> 00:57:48.300
- How do you feel about Mandy now?

768
00:57:48.300 --> 00:57:51.043
- I feel worse, so thanks for that.

769
00:57:51.880 --> 00:57:52.780
- [Lemonade] Why?

770
00:57:52.780 --> 00:57:54.363
- I wanted her to hear me,

771
00:57:55.510 --> 00:57:57.560
and understand what I went through.

772
00:57:57.560 --> 00:58:01.390
