to me. I was just so angry.


773
00:58:01.390 --> 00:58:03.220
I poured everything into our friendship

774
00:58:03.220 --> 00:58:05.180
and now it's nothing!

775
00:58:05.180 --> 00:58:07.370
Somewhere deep down inside
she had to have known


776
00:58:07.370 --> 00:58:08.909
that I was doing something to protect

777
