and the people that threatened her.

781
00:58:18.370 --> 00:58:20.350
I stood up for her. 
You were right before.

782
00:58:20.350 --> 00:58:22.480
What did she ever really do for me?

783
00:58:22.480 --> 00:58:24.153
- So she deserved what she got.

784
00:58:26.070 --> 00:58:28.210
- No. No, that's not what I'm saying.

785
00:58:28.210 --> 00:58:31.509
I hate what she did. I
hate that she lied to me.


786
00:58:31.509 --> 00:58:33.623
Now I don't know
what was true or not.

787
00:58:34.670 --> 00:58:36.610
What if she lied about other things?

788
00:58:36.610 --> 00:58:38.700
- So do you think she
felt guilty for the things


789
