that she did?

790
00:58:40.310 --> 00:58:41.610
- I guess I'll never know.

791
00:58:42.830 --> 00:58:45.770
Took her getting drunk
to tell me, so, maybe?


792
00:58:45.770 --> 00:58:46.970
- I don't think she did.

