By the way, I miss you so much.

837
01:01:46.480 --> 01:01:48.523
Please take my pathetic ass back.

838
01:01:49.830 --> 01:01:52.230
Well, every time I was on a visitation,

839
01:01:52.230 --> 01:01:54.582
you give me some shitty
TV dinner, ignore me,


840
01:01:54.582 --> 01:01:57.890
and beat me until you
were sure I would bruise.


841
01:01:57.890 --> 01:01:59.081
You're my dad!

842
01:01:59.081 --> 01:01:59.914
- You know I hate that!

843
01:01:59.914 --> 01:02:00.940
- You're supposed to protect me!

844
01:02:02.670 --> 01:02:04.873
I was afraid of those weekends.

845
01:02:06.850 --> 01:02:08.780
Just waiting for you to hit me

846
01:02:08.780 --> 01:02:11.940
with that smile on your
face, and then you'd tell me,


847
01:02:11.940 --> 01:02:13.753
I was your best girl.

848
01:02:15.590 --> 01:02:18.770
I almost wanted it, because at the end,

849
01:02:18.770 --> 01:02:21.133
you would actually say
something nice to me.


850
01:02:23.611 --> 01:02:26.530
At least mom finally figured
out what you were doing.


851
01:02:28.247 --> 01:02:29.693
Do you regret anything now?

852
01:02:31.742 --> 01:02:33.790
- I regret the way things
ended between me and your mom.


853
01:02:33.790 --> 01:02:35.020
- That's not what I'm talking about.

854
01:02:35.020 --> 01:02:37.910
Do you regret anything
that you did to me?

855
01:02:37.910 --> 01:02:40.170
- No. You're my best girl.

856
01:02:40.170 --> 01:02:42.310
You are who you are because of me.

857
01:02:43.380 --> 01:02:46.363
- You don't get to take credit
for me. I'm my own person.


858
01:02:50.730 --> 01:02:53.523
- You are exactly like me.

859
01:02:53.523 --> 01:02:56.740
You and I, we hurt the
ones we love the most.


860
01:02:56.740 --> 01:02:59.299
I hurt you because I love you.

861
01:02:59.299 --> 01:03:02.100
I tried to give you your
parents back. A stable home.


862
01:03:02.100 --> 01:03:03.800
- That's not how you love someone.

863
01:03:04.940 --> 01:03:07.103
- You want love without pain.

864
01:03:08.150 --> 01:03:09.053
You won't find it.

865
01:03:22.120 --> 01:03:25.262
- You can't leave. 
You're too weak.

866
01:03:25.262 --> 01:03:28.040
(Ashley coughs)

867
01:03:28.040 --> 01:03:31.043
- Yeah, no shit. 
You did this to me.

868
01:03:32.323 --> 01:03:33.993
I think I passed out.

869
01:03:35.070 --> 01:03:40.070
I just wanna lay down in bed
and hope you go away. (coughs)


870
01:03:41.660 --> 01:03:43.910
- [Lemonade] You took
their lives. Look at them.


871
01:03:43.910 --> 01:03:46.070
- Stop!
- Was it worth it?


872
01:03:46.070 --> 01:03:46.903
- No!

873
01:03:52.378 --> 01:03:54.540
I didn't want Mandy to go
through what I went through.


874
01:03:54.540 --> 01:03:56.400
All I did was
make this worse for myself.

875
01:03:56.400 --> 01:03:59.873
I regretted it every day
and I can't take it back.


876
01:04:01.160 --> 01:04:03.203
I never thought about
it until I met you.

877
01:04:05.710 --> 01:04:07.577
- What made me so different?

878
01:04:15.683 --> 01:04:17.480
- Oh, hi! You're up!
(upbeat music)


879
01:04:17.480 --> 01:04:20.730
Ooh! We have lots of celebrating to do!

880
01:04:21.937 --> 01:04:23.354
- Celebrate what?

881
01:04:25.090 --> 01:04:27.163
- Sorry, I've already had a few!

882
01:04:28.477 --> 01:04:30.250
- You wanna tell me what's going on?

883
01:04:30.250 --> 01:04:32.990
- First, a toast to us.

884
01:04:32.990 --> 01:04:33.823
Drink up!

885
01:04:38.340 --> 01:04:40.493
- Happy two month anniversary!

886
01:04:41.770 --> 01:04:42.603
- What?

887
01:04:46.550 --> 01:04:51.170
- So, I know you have some
trouble with doing your nails


888
01:04:51.170 --> 01:04:53.133
so, I got you this.

889
01:04:54.610 --> 01:04:55.943
Do you like it?

890
01:04:55.943 --> 01:04:59.133
- This is actually perfect. Thank you.

891
01:05:00.020 --> 01:05:01.533
- I'm so glad you like it!

892
01:05:03.300 --> 01:05:04.363
- Two months, huh?

893
01:05:06.150 --> 01:05:08.150
Sorry, I don't think I got you anything.

894
01:05:09.420 --> 01:05:12.673
- Silly, you got me this dress!

895
01:05:13.910 --> 01:05:18.523
- I did? I'm
sorry, my head feels fuzzy.

896
01:05:19.423 --> 01:05:20.936
I don't remember.

897
01:05:20.936 --> 01:05:23.590
I don't even think I
can stand up right now.


898
01:05:23.590 --> 01:05:25.402
- That's okay. 
I'll come to you.

899
01:05:25.402 --> 01:05:28.069
(Ashley coughs)

900
01:05:31.908 --> 01:05:33.370
- This is nice.

901
01:05:33.370 --> 01:05:34.270
- Yeah?

902
01:05:34.270 --> 01:05:37.751
- Yeah. You don't know
how much I've needed this.


903
01:05:37.751 --> 01:05:38.731
- Needed what?

904
01:05:38.731 --> 01:05:40.183
- Not holding back.

905
01:05:40.183 --> 01:05:42.433
I've kept almost everyone
else at a distance.


906
01:05:43.680 --> 01:05:45.230
- Then don't hold back with me.

907
01:05:49.685 --> 01:05:52.370
- I don't know what
I did to deserve you.

908
01:05:52.370 --> 01:05:54.100
I've felt like a part
of me was missing ever


909
01:05:54.100 --> 01:05:55.443
since my dad died.

910
01:05:57.140 --> 01:05:59.990
- You mean when you killed him?

911
01:05:59.990 --> 01:06:01.790
You don't have to hide that from me.

912
01:06:03.180 --> 01:06:04.013
- I don't mean to.

913
01:06:04.013 --> 01:06:06.807
It's just not something
I talk about a lot.


914
01:06:08.261 --> 01:06:10.150
He was a terrible person and a drunk,

915
01:06:10.150 --> 01:06:12.950
but I didn't kill him on purpose.

916
01:06:12.950 --> 01:06:14.520
- I'm sure you were scared.

917
01:06:14.520 --> 01:06:15.680
- It was a blur.

918
01:06:15.680 --> 01:06:17.263
One moment he was on
top of me, and the next,


919
01:06:17.263 --> 01:06:20.260
he wasn't moving, but I didn't mean to...

920
01:06:20.260 --> 01:06:21.463
- Look at me.

921
01:06:22.360 --> 01:06:24.410
That doesn't change how I feel about you.

922
01:06:25.400 --> 01:06:26.747
That doesn't define you.

