away as soon as it started.


957
01:09:16.780 --> 01:09:19.753
You made everything spin out of control.

958
01:09:21.390 --> 01:09:22.323
- Why me?

959
01:09:24.113 --> 01:09:26.157
- You were the first person I killed

960
01:09:26.157 --> 01:09:28.943
who was undoubtedly innocent.

961
01:09:31.470 --> 01:09:33.000
- I'm not that innocent.

962
01:09:35.360 --> 01:09:38.013
You've so much on your
shoulders for so long.


963
01:09:39.210 --> 01:09:41.593
Let me help you.

964
01:09:51.980 --> 01:09:54.310
- [Grandmother] Ashley, is that you?

965
01:09:54.310 --> 01:09:56.440
Were you talking to someone?

966
01:09:56.440 --> 01:09:59.763
I'm not feeling so well,
keep it down please.


967
01:10:07.480 --> 01:10:09.060
- What are you gonna do about her?

968
01:10:09.060 --> 01:10:10.800
- Grandma? Nothing.

969
01:10:10.800 --> 01:10:13.670
- She's been turning a blind
eye to what you've been doing.


