981
01:10:57.870 --> 01:10:59.643
No one's perfect, Ash.

982
01:11:00.670 --> 01:11:04.070
The trick is learning to
live with what you've done.


983
01:11:04.070 --> 01:11:06.963
No one is innocent, not any more.

984
01:11:08.280 --> 01:11:10.820
You're losing your chance
to become something better


985
01:11:10.820 --> 01:11:12.220
than what you lived through.

986
01:11:13.130 --> 01:11:15.493
You've lost your chance for forgiveness.

987
01:11:18.450 --> 01:11:19.420
You took away the chance

988
01:11:19.420 --> 01:11:24.420
from Paul, Rich, Brad,
Dean, Mat, Mandy, and myself


989
01:11:26.140 --> 01:11:27.813
to become better than we were.

990
01:11:28.750 --> 01:11:31.767
You took away the possibility
of what we could have been.


991
01:11:31.767 --> 01:11:34.503
And now you can't live
with who you are any more.


992
01:11:36.270 --> 01:11:39.903
All you can do is accept your
guilt and embrace your fate.


993
01:11:42.060 --> 01:11:45.263
- I want this to stop.
- You can make it stop.


994
01:11:47.800 --> 01:11:48.633
- Ashley!

995
01:11:50.370 --> 01:11:51.990
- Let me do this, Lemonade.

996
01:11:51.990 --> 01:11:53.520
