997
01:11:53.520 --> 01:11:54.610
It's Mandy.

998
01:11:54.610 --> 01:11:57.615
- Yeah okay, you're dead.

999
01:11:57.615 --> 01:11:59.515
- You sound so
happy to see I'm alive.

1000
01:12:00.610 --> 01:12:02.000
- Is it really you?

1001
01:12:02.000 --> 01:12:04.203
- Yes. I came to get even.

1002
01:12:05.110 --> 01:12:06.808
But I can see you've
already done it to yourself.


